value.name: Ultraman New Generation Stars
value.original_name: ウルトラマン ニュージェネレーション スターズ
value.overview: When memories of Ultra Heroes are erased by a mysterious entity, a device called Dimensionizer is sent from the future dimension Ultraman Decker is from. Trying to get memories of the Land of Light residents back, New Generation Heroes remember all their battles and hardships they've gone through.
